- Analyse Licensing of the Data Source
The publisher of both of the used datasets is the City Council of Madrid and the
rightsholder is the Direccin General de Planificacin e Infraestructuras de Movilidad.
The data has an open license that allows to reuse it for commercial and non-commercial
purposes, as long as the following conditions are met:
1. The sense of the information is not altered.
2. The source of the information is cited.
3. The date of the last update of the information is mentioned, as long as it was
included in the original document.
4. It is not insinuated that the City Council of Madrid supports or participates in the
reutilization of the data.
5. The metadata about the update date and the conditions for reuse are not altered or
deleted.
6. In the case of anonymized data for personal data protection purposes, the
concerning people are not re-identified by using other sources.
This license can be found here: https://datos.madrid.es/egob/catalogo/aviso-legal
The license we should use for the dataset generated should be of the same kind.
- Define Resource Naming Strategy
URI form: we use hash form for everything except for some datatype properties obtained
from other ontologies found (dbpedia-owl (ns3) and mv (ns4)).
URI Domain: http://grupo12_open_data.org#
Ontology path: group12/ontology/grupo12_open_data
o Classes: http://grupo12_open_data.es/lcc/resource#[className]
o Properties:
o Data Type Properties:
Dbpedia-owl: https://dbpedia.org/ontology/[propertyName]
Mv: http://schema.mobivoc.org/[propertyName]
Schema: http://schema.org#[propertyName]
Owl: http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#[propertyName]
Clase: http://grupo12_open_data.org#[propertyName]
Clase2:
http://grupo12_open_data.es/lcc/resource#[propertyName]
o Object Type Properties:
http://grupo12_open_data.es/lcc/resource#[propertyName]
o Individuals: http://grupo12_open_data.org#/resource/[propertyName]/[identifier]
Examples:
o Classes: http://grupo12_open_data.es/lcc/resource#ParkingFacility
o Properties (object type):
http://grupo12_open_data.es/lcc/resource#hasOccupancy
o Individuals:
http://grupo12_open_data.org#/resource/ParkingSpace/CAMARENA-1-1
